<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .content {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #ff0000;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 15px 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background-color: #cc0000;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="logo">
    <img width="200px" height="200px"
         src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/The-funny-team/inctagram-backend/78ea41511a1a5f5dc116ceeed08ce78e8a021575/apps/notifier/src/email/templates/logo.webp"
         alt="Company logo">
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <h1>Password recovery</h1>
    <p>Hello, {{name}}!</p>
    <p>You requested a password recovery on our website. To set a new password, please click on the button
      below.</p>
    <p><a href="{{resetLink}}" class="button">Reset password</a></p>
    <p>If you did not request a password recovery, ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Sincerely,<br>The Snapix team</p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>